Users : user_id, name, mail

Question_1 : Write SQL Query to find users whose email addresses contain only lowercase letters before the @ symbol

select user_id, name, mail
from Users
where mail regexp '^[a-z]+@[a-z]+.[a-z]+$';




Question_2 : Find email that has lowercase and numbers before the @ symbol!

select user_id, name, mail
from Users
where mail regexp '^[a-z.0-9]+@[a-z]+.[a-z]+$';
